PART 8: PARAMETRIC DEFORMATION — FROM F_p TO H(T)
======================================================================

prod(a + Q_k) = a^m · B_m(1/a) = a^m · U_m(1 + 1/(2a))

At a=2: prod(2+Q_k) = 2^m · B_m(1/2) = 2^m · U_m(5/4)
At a=1: prod(1+Q_k) = B_m(1) = U_m(3/2) = F_p
At a→∞: prod(a+Q_k) → a^m (trivial)

